In this screen you can list your ToDo tasks. You can access to edit screens by touching them. \n\nYou can create new ToDo tasks by touching button at bottom right. \n\nYou can filter, sort and search with the toolbar at the top. \n\nAlso you can access menu from that toolbar. ToDo tasks on dashboard, Sub Task on details screen and category list items supports swipe actions. \n\nIf you swipe to right you can DELETE and if you swipe to left you can COMPLETE those items. \n\nYou can undo the delete and restore ToDo tasks in few seconds You can edit account information and save your guest accounts in this screen. \n\nAlso you can edit your category list in this screen. \n\nYou can change application theme in this screen as well. &appname; is a cloud based application so you need an account to use. However it supports guest accounts to ease the first time user experience. \n\nIf you are going to use the app for a while, you should save your guest accounts because you can\'t access them after logging off. \n\nYou can save your guest accounts in settings screen.
&appname;, is a cloud based to do list application. You can take detailed notes with sub-items and easily track them here. \n\n&appname; is a cloud based app so you can reach all of your datas without any delay if you create an account. \n\nApplication can run smoothly in case of connection loss but we don\'t suggest a long use without a connection. \n\nWe suggest you to read this tutorial before using the application.
